org.cloudgraph.recognizer

Class GraphRecognizerContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.recognizer.GraphRecognizerContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EvaluationContext

    public class GraphRecognizerContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements EvaluationContext
    Context which supports the evaluation or "recognition" of a given data graph by a binary expression tree, within the context of the expression syntax.

    A graph recognizer is required when query expressions are present which reference properties not found in the row key model for a target graph.

    Since:
    0.5.3
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
